{"tid":2066111,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【ready Fight!!!】 觀塘巴士的士相撞 兩司機落車打交被捕","createTime":"2020-06-16T05:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T06:24:08.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56807aeb48240601cc4a966022e7065348bb798a","tid":2066111,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"觀塘開源道與鴻圖道交界，昨晚11時許，一輛雙層九巴沿開源道中線往觀塘碼頭方向行駛，駛至近鴻圖道交界時，與快線一輛剛落客駛出的紅的發生輕微碰撞。兩名司機發生口角，繼而動武互毆致兩敗俱傷。56歲姓郭巴士司機腰部受傷，51歲姓陳的士司機眼部受傷，兩人由接報救護員送院。警員調查後，以涉嫌打架拘捕兩人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/16/EqU9fK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F16%2FEqU9fK.png&h=e3aef1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/16/NMDHcl.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F16%2FNMDHcl.png&h=da93ee2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/mohFRPbnrqgwBgu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.17173cdn.com%2F2fhnvk%2FYWxqaGBf%2Fcms3%2FmohFRPbnrqgwBgu.jpg&h=35c7bcae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1206f5a2313ce8b5b5b5c7c0e400629d3b9aae69","tid":2066111,"uid":282930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T05:28:14.000Z","msg":"DC9真係以為條路佢嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜柒都要爭要霸"},{"pid":"0d832b0e4742be2922010c2ab97fda01281842a7","tid":2066111,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"肯定係dc9硬cut"}]}